description: From Verona, NJ, Fall 2012 AM class. Love soccer, college football, and sports in general, along with everything about this school and this fraternity. Co-Oping with Coca-Cola and pretending to be an adult. THWg.
aspects: This fraternity has served as a second home since I first joined and I wouldn't trade my brothers for anything. Every time here is a good time. Gamedays, Formal/Semi-Formal, MCR, Watermelon Bust.
name: Phil Vetrano
